{"tid":1414351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長期罷工計劃研討","createTime":"2019-08-05T12:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T12:09:24.000Z","uid":298546,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"810b29bb74978222254bc3abfb139e4dacc31b13","tid":1414351,"uid":298546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:07:01.000Z","msg":"真心罷一日工 其實對經濟等影響唔大 <br />\n影響唔夠大 政府一定繼續唔理 <br />\n要有效 就應該計劃一下點樣做到長期罷工<br />\n無論係自發定被迫 日日都有咁8月5既罷工規模先有用<br />\n香港人肯罷一日 好多一定唔肯長期罷<br />\n所以可以思考下 點樣可以做到<br />\n例如學生做base 之後每日輪住唔同界別接力罷工 肯日日罷既就keep住日日罷<br />\n唔知可唔可行呢?"},{"pid":"d80ee967b4d65dc7c0936ac9023a6f887c44acc4","tid":1414351,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:07:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">200%令政府中央收皮(和平合法易過長期罷工)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1412496\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1412496</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span>"},{"pid":"6d03e663f53a52ef9c341dfc4d994538a784f47e","tid":1414351,"uid":222190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:07:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/05/200746_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F05%2F200746_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png&h=43795457&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/05/200747_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F05%2F200747_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png&h=f0d1cde4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/05/200748_41701c121d5e5439ab62a40b295045b8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F05%2F200748_41701c121d5e5439ab62a40b295045b8.png&h=cdf40f08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43a